# Manual Testing Guide for CSV Parser

This guide provides manual test cases that can be run to verify the CSV parser functionality. Each test includes the input, expected output, and how to verify it.

## Test Environment Setup

```javascript
// Load the CSV parser
const { parseCSV } = require('./csv-parser.js');

// Or in TypeScript:
// import { parseCSV } from './csv-parser';

// Copy-paste the test code into Node.js REPL or your IDE
```

