## Common Patterns

### Filter and Count
```javascript
const count = result
  .filter(row => row.status === 'active')
  .count();
```

### Filter and Sum
```javascript
const total = result
  .filter(row => row.category === 'food')
  .sum('amount');
```

### Filter and Average
```javascript
