## Edge Cases Handled

✓ Empty input → Empty result (no errors)  
✓ Only headers → Empty rows  
✓ Empty fields → null values  
✓ Large fields → Works fine  
✓ Many columns → Works fine  
✓ Unclosed quotes → Error recorded, parsing continues  
✓ Column mismatch → Error recorded, row skipped  
